stories.title: Pakistan fashion 49-run victory over Bangladesh at Chittagong
stories.summary: For the briefest of moments at Chittagong, home supporters must have glimpsed a pale parabola of joy as their bowlers broke through a Pakistani top-order fairly bristling with stalwart names
